beer.beer_description: Inspired by the citrus farms which ones populated the Hills Shire, we decided to make somethign a little unique. Combining mandarin, orange peel, coriander and salt to a wheat heavy malt bill with a touch of melanoidin malt for colour. We created a slightly tart, refreshing beer with a clean, light salt finish.
